      <section class="readme-section" id="setup-reference">
        <h2>Setup reference</h2>
        <p>If you need to bootstrap from scratch, keep these commands handy.</p>
        <div class="copy-grid">
          <article class="copy-card">
            <header>
              <h3>Daemon (one-time per machine)</h3>
              <p>Launches the tmux-managed process SweetLink uses for DevTools and automation.</p>
            </header>
            <div class="copy-row">
              <code id="ref-daemon">pnpm sweetlink:daemon</code>
              <button
                type="button"
                class="copy-btn copy-icon-btn"
