      <section>
        <h2>Manual walkthrough</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Confirm the daemon and demo server are running (see setup reference if needed).</li>
          <li>Click <strong>Re-run handshake</strong> or run the controlled open command to refresh the session.</li>
          <li>Use <code>pnpm sweetlink sessions</code> to copy the codename (for example <code>narrow-xylophone</code>).</li>
          <li>Execute the post-connect commands to manipulate the widgets or capture screenshots.</li>
          <li>Inspect telemetry with <code>pnpm sweetlink devtools console --tail 50</code> when debugging.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>
